ot only generated additional income but also significantly enhanced guest satisfaction. His hands-on approach and strategic mindset make him an invaluable asset to any organization.\n\nI wholeheartedly recommend Mr. Sujin for any similar role where his talents and leadership can continue to drive success.", "recommendations/0/name": "sujin photien", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Food and Beverage Hospitality", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sujin-photien-773a731a5/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAADAIl4cBSCW5-Nk-4mTZfcOzPvab6pgPm58", "recommendations/1/context": "Frederic was senior to Isaac but didn't manage Isaac directly", "recommendations/1/date": "July 20, 2024", "recommendations/1/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Isaac for several months at Holiday Inn Resort Phuket Karon Beach, and I can confidently say that he is one of the most exceptional General Managers I have ever encountered. Isaac possesses a unique blend of skills that make him an invaluable asset to any hotel property.\n\nIsaac’s expertise in business development is unparalleled. He has a keen eye for identifying growth opportunities and implementing strategies that drive revenue and enhance the guest experience. His strategic thinking and decision-making abilities have consistently led to impressive results, making him a key player in taking our property to the next level.\n\nMoreover, Isaac excels in team development. He is a natural leader who inspires and motivates his team, fostering a positive and productive work environment. His ability to build strong, cohesive teams is evident in the improved performance and morale of our staff.\n\nNetworking is another of Isaac’s strengths. He has an extensive network of industry contacts and is always willing to leverage these relationships to benefit the property. His creative personality and innovative approach to problem-solving have consistently brought fresh ideas and solutions to the table.\n\nIn summary, Isaac is a highly skilled and dedicated professional with the vision and capability to transform any hotel property. I highly recommend him for any General Manager position, confident that he will exceed expectations and deliver outstanding results.", "recommendations/1/name": "Isaac M", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "General Manager | Revenue Management | F&B | Performance Improvement", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/isaac-m-a03a1621/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAASZhyMBaQh8CCR-EWi8-THGdmhXUAsfzdI", "recommendations/2/context": "Frederic managed Thomas directly", "recommendations/2/date": "July 10, 2022", "recommendations/2/description": "I am very proud to have had the opportunity to work with Thomas. He has great adaptability, very well organized, energetic, autonomous, detailed oriented, does not count his hours, capable of meeting great challenges as well as leading a team of top performers. Thomas is very comfortable and perfectly masters the administrative side as much as the operational part of the job. He is a considerable asset in a dynamic team and he is full of potential. I recommend Thomas to any organization looking for a well established young professional capable of boosting your F&B operations within any hotel environment", "recommendations/2/name": "Thomas Joossen", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Directeur de N la plage Hôtel Le Negresco", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/thomas-joossen-a1b780120/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB4DobcBj4P0QzSWt77Bsxl0QGQ2keTubXk", "recommendations/3/context": "Frederic worked with Jihane on the same team", "recommendations/3/date": "July 27, 2020", "recommendations/3/description": "Working with Jihane has been a very enriching experience. She is experienced, innovative, passionate and has a perfect command of communication and advertising tools. Always ahead against the competition, she is able to measure the mar